{"tid":2071902,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"暗黑版潤娥出浴照曝光！胸前「完全不遮」　 網：這樣太危險～","createTime":"2020-06-20T07:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T12:13:07.000Z","uid":217211,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"473dcdf0c2d3cc5684137178a3310d19a32a672b","tid":2071902,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkNDU8m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkNDU8m.jpg&h=bfa59720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDJ Soda可以說是韓國性感的DJ的代表，不過近來不少DJ也緊追其後，尤其一名知名的DJ「MIU」更是受到許多矚目。DJ「MIU」本名叫美玲元(원미령暫譯)，因為長相神似網紅企鵝妹以及大勢偶像潤娥，因此有「暗黑版潤娥」、「暗黑企鵝妹」等封號。近日，她再度因為一張照片，而在網上引起熱議！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ki0ettt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKi0ettt.jpg&h=9d048c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHbhre9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHbhre9.jpg&h=a042cbb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近來因為疫情稍緩的關係，DJ「MIU」也趁著空閒的時間，到濟州島玩耍，並曬出多張福利照，讓一票網友大飽眼福！照片中，能看出DJ「MIU」的泳衣並沒有特殊的集中效果，不過由於她的上圍相當豐滿，所以雪白的胸前風光，仍是能看見明顯的線條，看起來相當誘人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHpyJ1V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHpyJ1V.jpg&h=3e0f6e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除此之外，在另一張照片中，DJ「MIU」雖然泡在泳池裡，不過她穠纖合度的大腿，在水裡若隱若現的樣子，相當吸睛。雖然上圍十分傲人，不過DJ「MIU」的四肢卻十分纖細，腹部更是明顯可見腹肌，身材相當健美。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmyWGOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmyWGOF.jpg&h=5b60b475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除此之外，DJ「MIU」也大方po出自己出浴的樣子，讓一票網友看得臉紅心跳。照片中，DJ「MIU」全身上下只圍著一條白色浴巾，頭髮全都向後撥，讓她的身材全都曝光在鏡頭前，姿態相當大方。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gmw5z8M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmw5z8M.jpg&h=f7e07c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPoGSVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPoGSVs.jpg&h=cf7335d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"